"If a user fails to sign in :setting:`AUTH_LOCK_ATTEMPTS` times, password "
"authentication will be turned off on the account until having gone through "
"the process of having its password reset."
msgstr ""
"Bir kullanıcı :setting:`AUTH_LOCK_ATTEMPTS` kez oturum açamazsa, parola "
