":http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/(string:component)/credits/` "
"and :http:get:`/api/projects/(string:project)/credits/` API endpoints for "
"components and projects."
msgstr ""
"Bileşenler ve projeler için :http:get:`/api/components/(string:project)/"
